**These are the Rules any Rule Breaking and you will be Punished** 
```1. No advertising of any type.
2. Be respectful to staff and admins
3. Spamming and immature behavior isn't allowed
4. Do Not post any NSFW materials anywhere but NSFW channels
5. If you need help ask a staff or admin(Don't Spam)
6. DO NOT post any confidential information. This includes but not limited to, IPs, Emails, Passwords, etc.
7. If you violate these rules, you may be WARNED/BANNED```
**Rules can be updated at any time so please make sure to check in on them.
Check pins**
